librcnb
------------------------------------------
librcnb is a library of ANSI C routines for fast encoding/decoding data into
and from a rcnb-encoded format. C++ wrappers are included, as well as the
source code for standalone encoding and decoding executables.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  librcnb-devel-1.0.0-1bl2
  librcnb1-1.0.0-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/rcnbapp/librcnb

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/rcnbapp/librcnb/archive/refs/tags/v1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack librcnb-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./librcnb-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/librcnb-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librcnb-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librcnb1-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librcnb-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(librcnb)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/librcnb.README
  /usr/share/doc/librcnb/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/librcnb/README

(librcnb1)
  /usr/bin/cygrcnb-1.dll

(librcnb-devel)
  /usr/include/rcnb/cdecode.h
  /usr/include/rcnb/cencode.h
  /usr/include/rcnb/decode.h
  /usr/include/rcnb/encode.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/librcnb/librcnb-config-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/librcnb/librcnb-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/librcnb.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/librcnb.pc

